# Chttrix ‚Äî Deep Authentication & Authorization Security Audit

> **Auditor:** Principal Security Engineer (AI)
> **Date:** 2026-03-04
> **Scope:** Authentication √ó Authorization √ó WebSocket √ó Data Isolation
> **Stack Audited:** Node.js/Express ¬∑ MongoDB/Mongoose ¬∑ JWT ¬∑ Socket.IO ¬∑ Refresh tokens (HttpOnly cookie)

---

