## SECTION 10 ‚Äî FINAL SECURITY RATING

| Security Category | Score | Primary Finding |
|---|---|---|
| **Authentication Architecture** | **7 / 10** | Solid JWT + refresh design, but OAuth token in URL is critical |
| **Authorization Safety** | **5 / 10** | `checkRole` is broken, `conversation:join` unguarded, no brute force lockout |
| **WebSocket Security** | **6 / 10** | Handshake is correct; room-join authorization is missing |
| **Token Management** | **7 / 10** | Rotation and hashing are solid; cookie flags need verification |
