## VULNERABILITY SUMMARY

### CRITICAL

| ID | File | Description |
|---|---|---|
| C-1 | `auth.routes.js:227,318` | OAuth access token in URL query string ‚Äî logged and leaked |
| C-2 | `auth.controller.js` login | `failedLoginAttempts` and `lockedUntil` fields defined but never enforced ‚Äî unlimited brute force |
| C-3 | `permissionMiddleware.js:checkRole` | Reads `companyRole` from JWT payload, but JWT never contains that field ‚Äî middleware always 403s or is bypassed |

### HIGH

| ID | File | Description |
|---|---|---|
| H-1 | `auth.controller.js:626` | Refresh token returned in JSON response body ‚Äî defeats HttpOnly cookie |
| H-2 | `server.js:239‚Äì242` | Dashboard namespaces mounted without server-level `requireAuth` ‚Äî no defense-in-depth |
| H-3 | `messages.socket.js:31` | `conversation:join` has zero authorization ‚Äî any user joins any channel or DM room |
| H-4 | `socket.js:108` + `messages.socket.js:105` | Legacy `chat:join` has zero authorization |
| H-5 | `manager-dashboard.routes.js:314` | `Workspace.find()` without company scope ‚Äî cross-tenant data exposure |

### MEDIUM

| ID | File | Description |
|---|---|---|
| M-1 | `server.js:117` | `/refresh` and `/users` excluded from rate limiting |
| M-2 | `auth.routes.js:242` | LinkedIn OAuth state uses `Math.random()` ‚Äî weak CSRF protection |
| M-3 | `auth.controller.js:441` | OTP codes stored in plaintext in MongoDB |
| M-4 | `auth.controller.js:712` | 30s grace period on old refresh token creates reuse window |
| M-5 | `auth.controller.js` | Session cap enforced only at login, not at refresh ‚Äî unbounded token accumulation |
| M-6 | `permissions.js:107` | Personal users not blocked from company workspaces when `companyId` is null |
| M-7 | `socket.js:73` | `company:join` has no company membership verification |
| M-8 | Auth POST endpoints | No CSRF protection on cookie-reliant endpoints |
| M-9 | `auth.js` middleware | Suspended user access tokens remain valid for up to 15 minutes |

### LOW

| ID | File | Description |
|---|---|---|
| L-1 | `permissionMiddleware.js` + `permissions.js` | Duplicate permission systems ‚Äî maintenance risk |
| L-2 | `auth.routes.js:35` | Two different import paths for `requireAuth` ‚Äî verify they resolve to same file |
| L-3 | `owner-dashboard.routes.js:192` | `complianceScore: 95` hardcoded ‚Äî misleading placeholder in production UI |

