## PRIORITY REMEDIATION ORDER

1. **[C-2]** Implement brute-force lockout in the login controller (fields already exist in the model)
2. **[C-1]** Change OAuth redirects to URL fragment (`#access=token`)
3. **[H-3 + H-4]** Add channel/DM membership checks to `conversation:join` and `chat:join`
4. **[C-3]** Fix `checkRole` ‚Äî include `companyRole` in JWT or fetch from DB
5. **[H-1]** Remove `refreshToken` from login JSON response body
6. **[H-2]** Apply `requireAuth` at server-level mount for all dashboard namespaces
7. **[H-5]** Scope `Workspace.find()` by `companyId` in manager dashboard
8. **[M-7]** Add company membership check to `company:join` socket event
9. **[M-2]** Replace `Math.random()` with `crypto.randomBytes()` for OAuth state
10. **[M-3]** Hash OTP codes before storing in MongoDB
